text: Lycée Henri Wallon is a senior high school/sixth-form college in Aubervilliers, Seine-Saint-Denis, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. As of 2017, there are more than 2000+ students in Lyceé Collège Henri Wallon Aubervilliers.
